high_descs: Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the microwave.
Take the potato out of the microwave.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the potato in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean potato.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the clean potato inside on the top shelf, then close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the microwave on the counter to the right.
Pick up the potato from inside the microwave and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the potato inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the black fridge on the left.
Put the rinsed potato on the middle shelf on the right side inside the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed potato in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn left for one step, turn right and walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, take the potato out and then shut the door.
Turn around and take one step, turn right and face the sink.
Put the potato in the sink at the bottom left right corner, turn on the water for a few seconds then turn off and take the potato out of the sink.
Turn around and walk four steps, turn left to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door, put the potato on the top shelf, situated on the top of the bottle on the shelf below, and then shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato in the refrigerator.
